Enum TaxonomicStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TaxonomicStatus>
      • org.gbif.api.vocabulary.TaxonomicStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TaxonomicStatus>
    public enum TaxonomicStatus
extends Enum<TaxonomicStatus>
    The taxonomic status of a taxon. For synonyms more detailed status values are provided which "subclass" synonym.
    See Also:
    rs.gbif.org vocabulary
